OL,3,CStudent loan survey: Ex-students say
OL,4,Cimpact of loan worse than expected
OL,6,FA government survey of former students
OL,7,Fwho took out a student loan has found
OL,8,Fthe majority feel the financial impact
OL,9,Fof repaying was worse than they
OL,10,Fexpected.
OL,12,FMore than 52,000 people responded to
OL,13,Fan online questionnaire by the
OL,14,FTreasury Committee about student loans
OL,15,Fand graduate taxation, with 49,357
OL,16,Frespondents having personally taken
OL,17,Fout a government loan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779898263
OL,3,CStudent loan survey: Ex-students say
OL,4,Cimpact of loan worse than expected
OL,6,FAround 82% of those respondents said
OL,7,Fthat the financial impact of the
OL,8,Fstudent loan repayments had been worse
OL,9,Fthan they anticipated, with even more
OL,10,Fstating that the levels of interest
OL,11,Fand repayment terms were unreasonable.
OL,13,FMore than half of respondents said
OL,14,Fthey would not take out a loan again
OL,15,Fknowing what they know now, while more
OL,16,Fthan 90% also acknowledged they would
OL,17,Fnot have been able to attend
OL,18,Funiversity without it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779898263
OL,3,CStudent loan survey: Ex-students say
OL,4,Cimpact of loan worse than expected
OL,6,FThe public questionnaire were also
OL,7,Fasked how informed students felt when
OL,8,Ftaking out the loan.
OL,10,FOf those students who did take out a
OL,11,Floan, 57% said they did not understand
OL,12,Fthe terms of conditions of the loan
OL,13,Fbefore taking them out and 70%
OL,14,Fresponding their loan repayments had a
OL,15,Fmaterial impact on their financial
OL,16,Fplanning for the future.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
