OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779898263
OL,3,CStudent loan survey: Ex-students say
OL,4,Cimpact of loan worse than expected
OL,6,FAs part of its inquiry into student
OL,7,Floans, the Treasury Committee also
OL,8,Fpublished some of the promotional
OL,9,Fmaterial issued by the Department for
OL,10,FEducation.
OL,12,FThe material, which includes video
OL,13,Fexplainers, presentations on student
OL,14,Ffinance and FAQ pages, will be used by
OL,15,Fthe committee as evidence whether the
OL,16,Floans were properly explained and
OL,17,Fadvertised to prospective students.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779898263
OL,3,CStudent loan survey: Ex-students say
OL,4,Cimpact of loan worse than expected
OL,6,FThe material published by successive
OL,7,Fgovernments between 2018 and 2026
OL,8,Ffocusses on how student loans differ
OL,9,Fto commercial and bank loans.
OL,11,FWatch: Department for Education's 2019
OL,12,Fguide to student finance
OL,14,FOne PowerPoint presentation,
OL,15,Fdistributed to schools in 2018,
OL,16,Fexplicitly states how the loans are
OL,17,F"designed to make sure repayments
OL,18,Falways remain manageable and
OL,19,Faffordable."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779898263
OL,3,CStudent loan survey: Ex-students say
OL,4,Cimpact of loan worse than expected
OL,6,FOther FAQ documents answer questions
OL,7,Flike "Will my student loan affect my
OL,8,Fability to get a mortgage in future?"
OL,9,Fand "I'm worried I'm going to have a
OL,10,Flifetime of debt I'll never be able to
OL,11,Frepay."
OL,13,FThe materials focus on reassuring
OL,14,Fstudents that it "is unlikely to
OL,15,Fimpact materially on an individual's
OL,16,Fability to get a mortgage" and how the
OL,17,Floans are written off after 30 years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
