FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779898263
OL,3,CStudent loan survey: Ex-students say
OL,4,Cimpact of loan worse than expected
OL,6,FThe Treasury Committee launched an
OL,7,Finquiry into student loans following
OL,8,Foutcry around the repayment of Plan 2
OL,9,Floans.
OL,11,FPlan 2 loans, which an estimated 5.8
OL,12,Fmillion people took out between 2012
OL,13,Fand 2023, have proved controversial as
OL,15,Fthe interest on the loan is tied to
OL,16,Finflation - which means students are
OL,17,Frepaying a loan which is getting
OL,18,Fbigger with inflation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779898263
OL,3,CStudent loan survey: Ex-students say
OL,4,Cimpact of loan worse than expected
OL,6,FCoupled with chancellor Rachel Reeve's
OL,7,Fdecision to freeze the salary at which
OL,8,Fgraduates start paying back their
OL,9,Fstudent loans means that, as wages
OL,10,Frise, more people are hitting the
OL,11,Fthreshold and starting to repay their
OL,12,Floans sooner.
OL,14,FResponding to the survey results,
OL,15,FChair of the Treasury Committee, Dame
OL,16,FMeg Hillier said the findings show
OL,17,Fmany former students feel "over-
OL,18,Fburdened and demoralised" by their
OL,19,Fdebt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779898263
OL,3,CStudent loan survey: Ex-students say
OL,4,Cimpact of loan worse than expected
OL,6,FMeg Hillier explains that although 39%
OL,7,Fof students will pay off their loan,
OL,8,Fit has great impacts for many.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News, Hillier said:
OL,11,F"We heard very clearly the anger that
OL,12,Fpeople felt about the impact this is
OL,13,Fhaving on their lives."
OL,15,FFocussing on the age group impacted,
OL,16,Fshe added: "We need to be treating
OL,17,Fthis group of 20-30 somethings better
OL,18,Fbecause they are the engine room of
OL,19,FBritain."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779898263
OL,3,CStudent loan survey: Ex-students say
OL,4,Cimpact of loan worse than expected
OL,6,FThe committee itself is limited in the
OL,7,Factions it can take but she hoped
OL,8,Fmembers could make some
OL,9,Frecommendations to the government.
OL,11,FThe Treasury Committee will hear
OL,12,Fevidence from student and university
OL,13,Frepresentatives, as well as Sir Philip
OL,14,FAugar who wrote the review into
OL,15,Fstudent loans in 2019.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
